<br>
If a sexy girl smiles at you, do you assume that means she wants you to walk over and kiss her on the throat right now?  I suspect not.  First, you'll find out if that was really an invitation.  Perhaps her friend told her a witicism while she was glancing your way.  Perhaps her boyfriend walked in the door behind you.  Who knows?  Certainly not you at this point.  So, you find out.<br>
<br>
Same thing here with the /roleplay flag.  You have at least a 1:5 chance of the person being receptive to RP or at the very least aware of it and able to recognize your efforts.  But, some just have no clue and don't even have the foggiest about RP.  So, stalk your intended RP victim with a little finnesse before you bend her backwards and plant your fangs. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gothmatum>Gothmatum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/18/03 8:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3885.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://users.zoominternet.net/~gothmatum/images/eqpagoth.gif width=93 height=177></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: /roleplay?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>It was enough to start a war between Vanu Soverignity and the New Conglomerate..ok not really, but for all intents and purposes. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
