<br>
I don't use the roleplay tag. This is so that if someone does happen to want to group with me, or happen to want a chance run-by encounter, they can see where I am. Sure, they can ask. But it's not the same. <br>
<br>
Don't judge someone as not being a roleplayer just because they don't use the roleplay tag. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
I also assume that *everyone* on this server is here for roleplay. Even if they don't. Especially if they don't. Then they get a large order of roleplay, with a side of french fries and a chocolate milkshake. Convert the heathens!<br>
<br>
